      • confirm

        public void confirm()
        This method is run when the confirm button is pressed on the supplier form, the method then gets the relevant information from the user input, creates a new supplier from it, and then adds it to an instance of Business. It also gives back informational feedback to the user to inform them that the supplier has been added successfully.
